  <item>
    <title>Homage: Beginning</title>
    <link>http://quietlittlelies.com/exercise/queneauvian-1-beginning</link>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;Show me the way it might start:&lt;br /&gt;
A writer imagines the banal—&lt;br /&gt;
Two chance encounters with some chap, two hours apart—&lt;br /&gt;
Now he’s in the story’s thrall!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;He sets himself a trial&lt;br /&gt;
That will test his strength and guile:&lt;br /&gt;
Tell the same tale in some 99 ways;&lt;br /&gt;
That’s &lt;em&gt;Exercises in Style!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
     <category domain="http://quietlittlelies.com/category/exercise-type/queneauvian">Queneauvian</category>
