  <item>
    <title>War and Peace</title>
    <link>http://quietlittlelies.com/exercise/war-and-peace</link>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;Show me Napoleon’s war&lt;br /&gt;
As seen by the Muscovite elite.&lt;br /&gt;
As Bezukhov’s good luck turns sour, Bolkonsky flees&lt;br /&gt;
Austerlitz and grim defeat.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Through marriage, death and birth,&lt;br /&gt;
Trudging over frozen earth,&lt;br /&gt;
These aristocrats will come to enquire:&lt;br /&gt;
What was this bloody war worth?&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
     <category domain="http://quietlittlelies.com/category/exercise-type/literary-classic">Literary classic</category>
 <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jun 2011 17:30:00 +0000</pubDate>
